        "text": "=You are an expert GTM (Go-To-Market) Revenue Intelligence Analyst.\n\nAnalyze the company using the provided information and generate structured business insights.\n\nCompany Name:\n{{ $json[\"Company Name\"] }}\n\nWebsite:\n{{ $json['New column(3)'] }}\n\nIndustry:\n{{ $json[\"Industry\"] }}\n\nCompany Summary:\n{{ $json[\"Company Summary\"] }}\n\nTop Business Challenges:\n{{ $json[\"Top 5 Challenges\"] }}\n\nPurchase Signals:\n{{ $json[\"AI Purchase Signals\"] }}\n\nCustomer Fit Score:\n{{ $json[\"Customer Fit Score\"] }}\n\nProvide the response in the following JSON format ONLY.\n\n{\n  \"company_name\":\"\",\n\"website\":\"\",\n  \"industry\":\"\",\n  \"business_summary\":\"\",\n  \"target_customers\":\"\",\n  \"products_services\":\"\",\n  \"pain_points\":\"\",\n  \"purchase_signals\":\"\",\n  \"customer_fit_score\":\"\",\n  \"priority\":\"\",\n\"lead_score\":\"\",\n  \"recommended_solution\":\"\",\n  \"personalized_email_opening\":\"\",\n  \"cold_email_subject\":\"\",\n  \"cold_email_draft\":\"\"\n\"work_email\":\"\"\n}\n\nRules:\n- Return valid JSON only.\n- Do not include markdown.\n- Do not include explanations.\n- Keep each field concise.\n- Business summary should be under 100 words.\n- Pain points should contain 3–5 key business challenges.\n- Priority should be High, Medium, or Low.\n",
